<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Cyber International Certificates</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #003366 50%, #00aaff 50%);
            color: white;
        }
        header {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 2em 1em;
            background-color: #003366;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
        }
        header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }
        .container {
            margin: 2em auto;
            padding: 20px;
            max-width: 1200px;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px;
        }
        .certificate {
            background: white;
            color: #003366;
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 6px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            overflow: hidden;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: space-between;
        }
        .certificate:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
        }
        .certificate h2 {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            margin: 1em;
        }
        .certificate p {
            margin: 0.5em 1em;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }
        .certificate strong {
            color: #00aaff;
        }
        .button-container {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: flex-end;
            margin: 1em;
        }
        .enroll-btn {
            padding: 12px;
            background-color: #00aaff;
            color: white;
            font-size: 1rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-align: center;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 10px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, transform 0.2s ease;
            width: 150px;
        }
        .enroll-btn:hover {
            background-color: #003366;
            transform: scale(1.05);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>Cyber International Certificates</h1>
    </header>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="certificate">
            <h2>Certified Information Systems Security Professional (CISSP)</h2>
            <p><strong>Description:</strong> CISSP is a globally recognized certification that validates your expertise in information security. It covers key areas like risk management, network security, security architecture, and access control, preparing you for roles such as security consultant or security manager.</p>
            <p><strong>Duration:</strong> Approximately 4-6 months of study, depending on your prior experience.</p>
            <p><strong>Cost:</strong> Exam fee is $749 USD.</p>
            <p><strong>How to Enroll:</strong> Visit the official ISC2 CISSP Certification page, create an account, and schedule your exam. You can also access study materials and practice tests on the same platform.</p>
            <div class="button-container">
                <a href="https://www.isc2.org/cissp" class="enroll-btn">Enroll Now</a>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="certificate">
            <h2>CompTIA Security+</h2>
            <p><strong>Description:</strong> CompTIA Security+ is an entry-level certification that validates your knowledge in IT security fundamentals, including network security, threat management, cryptography, and risk management.</p>
            <p><strong>Duration:</strong> Approximately 2-4 months of study, depending on your prior experience.</p>
            <p><strong>Cost:</strong> Exam fee is $370 USD.</p>
            <p><strong>How to Enroll:</strong> Visit the official CompTIA Security+ Certification page, create an account, and schedule your exam. Preparation materials and courses are available on the same platform.</p>
            <div class="button-container">
                <a href="https://www.comptia.org/certifications/security" class="enroll-btn">Enroll Now</a>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="certificate">
            <h2>Certified Ethical Hacker (CEH)</h2>
            <p><strong>Description:</strong> CEH certifies your skills in ethical hacking and penetration testing. It focuses on identifying vulnerabilities in systems and networks to help organizations secure their IT infrastructure against malicious attacks.</p>
            <p><strong>Duration:</strong> Approximately 3-6 months of study, depending on your prior experience.</p>
            <p><strong>Cost:</strong> Exam fee is $1,199 USD.</p>
            <p><strong>How to Enroll:</strong> Visit the official EC-Council CEH Certification page, create an account, and schedule your exam. Training courses and practice tests are available on the same platform.</p>
            <div class="button-container">
                <a href="https://www.eccouncil.org/programs/certified-ethical-hacker-ceh/" class="enroll-btn">Enroll Now</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>